README           this file

test-all.sh      Shell script to run Trilinos test harness with all *-input
                 files in this directory.

machine          jhu's machine-specific configure line options.

machine-mpi      jhu's machine-specific MPI configure line options.

XX-input         Input files for test-harness.plx perl script.  Each specifies
                 three files containing configure-line options:
                    machine      (include & library paths, etc.)
                    machine-mpi  (mpi-specific stuff)
                    XX-configure (package stuff)

standalone-configure
                 Enable ml only.

basic-configure  standalone plus
                 epetra, aztecoo, triutils

teuchos-configure basic plus
                 teuchos, amesos

partition-configure: teuchos plus
                 anasazi
                 zoltan, metis, & parmetis-3.x interfaces enabled
